Use CMake Targets

Fix buildpaths QA errors by backporting selected CMake changes to
use CMake targets.

Upstream-Status: Backport [https://github.com/ros-navigation/navigation2/commit/b6a5387d6823de6eb8008da995a72086e8ace1e5]

Signed-off-by: Rob Woolley <rob.woolley@windriver.com>

